The company was within its rights to cancel the deal. But LNG agreements wo=
rth hundreds of millions of dollars aren=E2=80=99t usually scrapped over a =
single payment dispute, or so quickly.=C2=A0

No no no, this agreement=C2=A0wasn=E2=80=99t=C2=A0scrapped over a single pa=
yment dispute! It was scrapped over, the price went up! Pakistan held back =
