: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  talked</a> a few <a href=3D"https://lin=
k.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/33697175.257398/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21i=
ZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMTItMDYvd2hvLWdldHMtcGFpZC1mb3Itbm9=
0LWN1dHRpbmctZG93bi10cmVlcz9jbXBpZD1CQkQxMjE0MjNfTU9ORVlTVFVGRiZ1dG1fbWVkaX=
