efs of society=E2=80=9D; and =E2=80=9Cmerchants,=E2=80=9D who are =E2=80=9C=
portly=E2=80=9D and =E2=80=9Cbearded,=E2=80=9D and include venture capitali=
sts and cryptocurrency professionals.</p>
